Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

09:06.168 --> 09:07.970
Oh, wow, that was pretty close.

09:07.977 --> 09:09.453
Close?

09:09.478 --> 09:13.133
Close?! It's called The Price Is Right,
not The Price Is Close!

09:13.145 --> 09:15.242
Oh, man, this is bad.

09:15.258 --> 09:17.693
If I don't win the spin-off, and I can't
get into the Showcase Showdown,

09:17.708 --> 09:19.720
everything's ruined!
It's all ruined!

09:19.726 --> 09:22.622
What is ruined?
Why, why is this such a big deal?

09:23.658 --> 09:27.630
Okay, guys... sit down,
I've got to tell you something.

09:30.206 --> 09:33.433
The reason I'm going on The Price Is Right

09:33.447 --> 09:37.750
is because I've decided that it's time
for me to meet my real father.

09:37.808 --> 09:39.801
- Your father?
- That's right.

09:41.826 --> 09:46.351
My father... is Bob Barker.

09:50.337 --> 09:53.040
- Your dad... is Bob Barker?
- That's right.

09:53.227 --> 09:55.620
The host of The Price Is Right,
Bob Barker?

09:55.638 --> 09:56.590
That's Pops.

09:56.877 --> 09:59.031
- Barney?
- Yes, Robin?

09:59.125 --> 10:01.992
Why in the world do you think
Bob Barker is your father?

10:02.027 --> 10:06.213
Uh, because my mother told me
he was, that's why.

10:06.648 --> 10:08.673
Mom, who's my dad?

10:08.775 --> 10:11.573
All the other kids at school
know who their dad is.

10:11.875 --> 10:14.772
- Who's mine?
- Oh, I don't know.

10:15.516 --> 10:16.913
That guy.

10:20.246 --> 10:22.891
Look, Dad, I got straight A's!

10:24.148 --> 10:27.640
Hey, Dad, guess who I'm going
as for Halloween?

10:28.506 --> 10:30.112
Want to play some catch, Pop?

10:34.085 --> 10:37.162
So now I'm gonna go to L.A.,
be on the show,

10:37.175 --> 10:38.731
win the Showcase Showdown,

10:38.745 --> 10:42.381
make him proud of me,
and then tell him who I am.

10:42.835 --> 10:47.181
You're gonna tell Bob Barker that
you're his son on national television?

10:47.275 --> 10:50.011
Why is this so hard for you
people to believe?

10:50.935 --> 10:52.251
Drop the popper!

10:52.535 --> 10:54.801
Lily has to gain five pounds
in a week and a half,

10:54.815 --> 10:57.080
and it is my job to help her get there.

10:57.165 --> 10:59.383
This is the best wedding diet ever.

11:00.257 --> 11:03.241
- I lost a pound.
- That is impossible.

11:03.258 --> 11:05.332
You ate McDonald's
every meal for three days.

11:05.347 --> 11:08.253
I knew that Super Size
Me guy was full of it.

11:08.515 --> 11:11.533
Well, it must be the wedding stress.
We just got to up the intake.

11:11.656 --> 11:14.772
Lily Aldrin, drop and give me
20 bites of fudge!

11:15.568 --> 11:16.552
Okay?

11:17.507 --> 11:19.441
Don't nibble at it.
Attack it!

11:20.076 --> 11:21.872
Come on, Lily.
You can do better than that!

11:21.876 --> 11:22.670
I can't.

11:22.675 --> 11:25.312
Well, eat faster, before
your body figures out it's full.

11:25.316 --> 11:28.512
I'm trying.
Oh, are you gonna cry?

11:28.676 --> 11:31.291
You gonna cry?
Skinny little baby's gonna cry?

11:31.306 --> 11:33.950
- Well, eat, damn it, eat!
- Okay!

11:38.538 --> 11:42.742
Hey, so I think I figured out how to do
your toast in a completely appropriate way.

11:42.758 --> 11:44.492
- Finally.
- Yeah.

11:45.558 --> 11:48.303
Good evening. I'm Ted Mosby,
Marshall's best man.

11:48.318 --> 11:49.361
- Still strong, right?
- Great, yeah.

11:49.376 --> 11:53.432
I'd like to share with you all a story
about the momentous evening last fall

11:53.447 --> 11:56.223
when Marshall and Lily got back together.

11:56.535 --> 11:59.943
Afterward, we stayed up
till 10:00 at night,

12:00.215 --> 12:04.760
- doing shots of chocolate milk.
- Man, I'm well nourished right now!

12:04.806 --> 12:07.280
Calcium promotes healthy teeth and bones.

12:07.326 --> 12:11.211
Thanks, Marshall, for teaching us
you don't need alcohol to have fun.

12:11.226 --> 12:15.412
Oh, don't thank me. Thank my parents
