- So, was it $1,350?

16:08.015 --> 16:09.212
I don't know.

16:09.525 --> 16:11.723
- Was it?
- Oh, my God!

16:12.116 --> 16:13.820
Happy wedding.

16:14.576 --> 16:18.913
Barney, you won that camcorder
in just one second!

16:18.916 --> 16:22.450
That is impressive.
I mean impressive.

16:22.466 --> 16:23.662
Thank you, Bob.

16:23.675 --> 16:27.883
