18:33.548 --> 18:37.761
Overbid!
Now, let's see Showcase #2.

18:38.106 --> 18:41.252
Barney, your showcase
begins with a mystery.

18:41.266 --> 18:42.921
Oh, I love this.

18:43.376 --> 18:45.493
I can't believe how excited I am right now.

18:46.977 --> 18:50.243
