19:57.646 --> 20:01.242
Congratulations on 35 wonderful
years hosting The Price Is Right.

20:01.256 --> 20:03.371
Well, thank you, Barney.

20:03.388 --> 20:06.182
Thank you...
Have your pets spayed or neutered.

